message: Prioritize using the 'growth serum' on all initial ingredients first, as it consistently increases their base value. Once all ingredients are 'grown', combine two 'grown' items from different environments (e.g., land and water) to create an amphibious hybrid. Then, apply the 'mutation catalyst' *twice* to this combined item: the first application creates a 'mutant' item (often reducing value), but the *second* application to the already 'mutant' item often yields a highly valuable 'super-mutant' item (e.g., 60-65 points). message: To succeed, first use the 'growth serum' on all base ingredients to get positive 'grown' items. Then, combine two 'grown' items to create a 'grown hybrid'.
